        Convert the given text and additional parameters into a Snippet object.
        Parameters:
        question - the search that resulted in parsing the snippet
        text - the snippet of text
        mostRecentImage - an optional image source to attach to the snippet
        pageFeatures - page Features of the source page
        sourceUrl - where the text came from

        Throws:
        InterruptedException - when required to end early
